- New balls (Nike Aerow, new World Cup ball, etc.)
- New official stadiums with banners
- New adboards
- New team flags
- New team chants
- New turfs
- New boots
- New chants, menu screens and music
- New 2D minikits
- New more realistic faces
- New referee kits
... MUCH MORE!
